{"tid":921892,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［殺手食評］- 愛文生飯店 撚手小菜","createTime":"2018-11-30T02:32:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T18:55:56.000Z","uid":221748,"like":16,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7d98082285237d9a3235744b59e1442c5bf67183","tid":921892,"uid":221748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:32:17.000Z","msg":"🇭🇰#香港捐窿捐罅記<br />\n大腿咁粗既豬手 配上黑椒汁果然係絕配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   好多人都中意去大排擋食 因為有鑊氣 同自由自在 可以做番自己 但大家又知唔知大排擋點解叫大排擋 <br />\n係50,60年代 政府見到香港經濟唔好 所以發d牌出去 等大家可以搞下食店 刺激下經濟 而政府發果個牌 比一般食店既牌大 所以就叫大排擋啦 現今香港大排擋主要係中環同深水埗 之後幾年前 政府又玩一牌兩制 只係比中環既大排擋傳比下一代 深水埗或其他地方既大排擋就唔比 所以少一間 就冇一間架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家想珍惜機會去食同去感受一下 香港舊時代既風味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-<br />\n黑椒鹹豬手 佢地主打菜 好大隻 厚肉地 但奇就奇在 好淋身 加上充滿骨膠原既皮 好味 再加上個算幾濃既黑椒汁 好滿足 大家去得食 記得要叫尼試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GhwCYcT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGhwCYcT.png&h=b65c128e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n椒鹽九肚魚 尼家應該係我食過 最好既九肚魚 因爲其實本身九肚身係冇味既  所以主要係靠個椒鹽味 同口感 佢椒鹽味夠 仲要炸得夠脆同硬身 配啤酒一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OOUXYcW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOOUXYcW.png&h=bc5a401e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n豉汁蒸鱔 我本身好中意食鱔既 所以見到英國人用尼整jelly eel真係浪費晒 食鱔其實最緊要條鱔新鮮  佢都做到 肉質彈口 配上豉汁加重返個味 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mzgfKSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmzgfKSZ.png&h=9e67ee00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總結來說 係一間高質大排擋 大家有機會應該去試下 不過記得早d去 因為好多人<br />\n-<br />\n🎈深水埗石硤尾街1號地下B-C號舖<br />\n-<br />\n平均傷害：$150<br />\n好味值：7/10 <br />\n<br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=2h8x5dalgni7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Ffoodkiller_dk%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3D2h8x5dalgni7&d=JxDRBE6j8SgAGaAZIKTA0dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=7aed8717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/foodkiller_dk?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=2h8x5dalgni7</a>"},{"pid":"b4e687f0fe15600472b3fcf7438181ee5b9f0740","tid":921892,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6f71752aecab35b9e32830903b2d0f7d5e86c2b","tid":921892,"uid":221748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b4e687f0fe15600472b3fcf7438181ee5b9f0740","tid":921892,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"我知呀 不過我得兩個人 所以冇叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有黃金蝦 炒聖子"},{"pid":"6dfc825c811c594beb3014de996571a3ce26e0df","tid":921892,"uid":131241,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b4e687f0fe15600472b3fcf7438181ee5b9f0740","tid":921892,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:07:03.000Z","msg":"薯仔牛柳粒萬發好食好多"},{"pid":"533fd8ed828d9a4e1cef18a6713ce4578cc867bc","tid":921892,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4e687f0fe15600472b3fcf7438181ee5b9f0740","tid":921892,"uid":144843,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T03:21:26.000Z","msg":"四周圍啲鋪都抄佢"},{"pid":"1c252ddc8b040961f97e491fce0f09d16bb023c4","tid":921892,"uid":221748,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"533fd8ed828d9a4e1cef18a6713ce4578cc867bc","tid":921892,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4e687f0fe15600472b3fcf7438181ee5b9f0740","tid":921892,"uid":144843,"like":5,"disli